I just remembered.

12
00:01:22,580 --> 00:01:24,940
What is the use now?

13
00:01:24,980 --> 00:01:27,530
What do you think you can you do with those memories?

14
00:01:27,530 --> 00:01:32,350
I just wanted you to know that I haven't forgotten your happy moments.

15
00:01:32,350 --> 00:01:36,070
No. I forgot all of them.

16
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:41,120
There are no happy memories of me loving you.

17
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:46,190
In my memories, you are just my past wound.

18
00:01:48,030 --> 00:01:52,530
I don't ever want to pull it out again.

19
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:59,490
Then let's start over from now. You don't need to bring the past to the surface.

20
00:01:59,490 --> 00:02:04,100
