21
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:22,850
♬ Always you will be the the person who is the same as a spring day for me ♬

22
00:02:22,850 --> 00:02:30,190
♬ I know you better than any one in the world. ♬

23
00:02:30,190 --> 00:02:39,000
♬ Now is the time I love you ... ♬

24
