This is the marketing concept for launching Cha Seo Hoo's charity concert and the shoes.

31
00:03:34,100 --> 00:03:39,600
Have you thoroughly analyzed whether Cha Seo Hoo will help our company, Team Leader Oh?

32
00:03:39,600 --> 00:03:43,480
If you get ahead of yourself again, you can bring huge damage to the company.

33
