37
00:04:00,270 --> 00:04:04,190
I will take responsibility for the ChaAndy Project.

38
00:04:14,220 --> 00:04:21,610
You really love responsibility. Good luck on your Mr. Cha Project.

39
00:04:22,540 --> 00:04:25,180
Yes. Thank you!

40
