First of all, the compensation regarding the cancellation of the performance

45
00:05:06,140 --> 00:05:08,360
will be taken care of by the company.

46
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:12,490
And...  their threat that they will interrupt your domestic activities

47
00:05:12,490 --> 00:05:15,640
seems to be real.

48
00:05:15,640 --> 00:05:18,600
- It was expected.
- What?

49
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:22,580
The biggest threat to me right now is something else.

50
00:05:30,510 --> 00:05:32,430
Hello.

51
00:05:34,600 --> 00:05:36,860
Am I here a bit early?

52
00:05:36,860 --> 00:05:38,660
Have a seat.

53
00:05:43,770 --> 00:05:45,300
This is amazing.

54
00:05:45,300 --> 00:05:48,670
Sharing Pianist Cha Seo Hoo's melody.

55
00:05:48,670 --> 00:05:51,810
It seems like the person who wrote this slogan has a lot of affection for me.

56
00:05:51,810 --> 00:05:53,470
Team Manager Oh is very...

57
00:05:53,470 --> 00:05:55,500
The concept for ChaAndy shoes advertisement

58
00:05:55,500 --> 00:05:59,870
is storytelling, including your performance, daily life,

59
00:05:59,870 --> 00:06:02,730
charity activities, and all other processes,

60
00:06:02,730 --> 00:06:06,710
creating an image that stimulates the audiences' emotions.

61
00:06:15,700 --> 00:06:19,590
Won! Choi Won!

62
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:26,330
Choi Won.

63
00:06:29,590 --> 00:06:31,500
What's wrong with you?

64
00:06:37,720 --> 00:06:40,630
Won! You have a fever.

65
00:06:40,630 --> 00:06:42,620
Are you sick?

66
00:06:44,260 --> 00:06:45,830
Let's go to the hospital, okay?

67
00:06:45,830 --> 00:06:47,330
Let's go.

68
00:06:47,330 --> 00:06:50,090
I'm okay. I'm okay.

69
00:06:52,370 --> 00:06:54,010
Won.

70
00:06:58,830 --> 00:07:04,970
Yes mom, I'm trying to make fish porridge. What goes in it?

71
00:07:06,130 --> 00:07:10,090
The refrigerator? Hold on.

72
00:07:10,090 --> 00:07:12,680
Yes it's here.

73
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:16,900
This... and green onions...

74
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:26,580
Oh right!

75
00:07:31,660 --> 00:07:34,320
Won, let's take medicine.

76
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:38,150
Aigoo!

77
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:18,160
Would this taste okay?

78
00:08:19,600 --> 00:08:21,640
It's done!

79
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:27,910
Wake up, Choi Won. Let's eat. Eat and then sleep.

80
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:31,590
Here.

81
00:08:31,590 --> 00:08:33,680
Are you possibly like this because of alcohol?

82
00:08:33,680 --> 00:08:39,400
If you're lying down sick like this all day, it hurts my, your friend's, heart.

83
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:40,810
Eat this and sleep.

84
00:08:40,810 --> 00:08:46,060
This is the medicine porridge that my mom cooks for me whenever I'm sick.

85
00:08:46,840 --> 00:08:50,680
But for a person whose heart hurts, you're too bright.

86
00:08:50,680 --> 00:08:53,170
Looking at you be all saucy, it seems like you have strength to eat.

87
00:08:53,170 --> 00:08:54,740
Here, eat.

88
00:08:55,790 --> 00:08:58,770
Is this edible?

89
00:08:58,770 --> 00:09:01,800
Hey, try it first.

90
00:09:01,800 --> 00:09:05,360
Test it first. Eat up.

91
00:09:14,120 --> 00:09:15,910
- Soy sauce.
- Soy sauce?

92
00:09:15,910 --> 00:09:18,800
Soy sauce. Hold on.

93
00:09:21,030 --> 00:09:23,560
Here, try it now.

94
00:09:29,220 --> 00:09:31,840
- Dried seaweed.
- Dried seaweed?

95
00:09:36,220 --> 00:09:38,200
More?

96
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:45,950
- Tissue.
- Hey!

97
00:09:45,950 --> 00:09:47,780
Don't eat it, don't eat it.

98
00:09:47,780 --> 00:09:50,520
I won't. It doesn't taste good. Take it.

99
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:53,930
Choi Won. Are you really sick?

100
00:09:53,930 --> 00:09:56,010
What really is wrong with you?

101
00:09:56,910 --> 00:10:01,130
And... I like beef porridge.

102
00:10:01,130 --> 00:10:03,740
- What?
- Make me beef porridge.

103
00:10:08,990 --> 00:10:13,110
Seriously, Choi Won. Once you get better...!

104
00:10:18,900 --> 00:10:21,180
Beef porridge?

105
00:10:24,910 --> 00:10:27,160
I've been too nice to him lately.

106
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:30,370
He's always teasing me when he has the opportunity.

107
00:10:30,370 --> 00:10:33,260
But why is he so sick?

108
00:10:36,800 --> 00:10:38,660
Where are you going again?

109
00:10:38,660 --> 00:10:41,710
To Won's house. Being sick alone is sad.

110
00:10:41,710 --> 00:10:43,590
I'm sad too.

111
00:10:43,590 --> 00:10:48,090
It's okay for me to be alone, but you're concerned about Won being alone?

112
00:10:51,890 --> 00:10:54,090
You're too much.

113
